SIYABONGA &nbsp;MKHWANAZI UNGQONGQOSHE wezeMpilo kuleli uDkt &nbsp;Aaron Motsoaledi usichaze njengo kuphanjanyelwa ingqondo isinyathelo sezikhulu zoMhyango wezeMpilo, eGoli sokususa iziguli ezigula ngengqondo eSidimeni, siziyise ezikhungweni ezizimele.UMotsoaledi izolo uphinde watshela iPhalamende ukuthi ukususwa kwalezi ziguli kwakugquqquzelwa imali.Uthe izikhulu zaseGoli nosopolitiki azikaze ziwutshele umnyango kazwelonke ukuthi yayingekho imali yokugcina lezi ziguli.&quot;Singasho singananazi ukuthi sikhathazekile futhi sidiniwe ngokufa kwalezi ziguli ezasuswa eSidimeni,&quot; kusho uMotsoaledi.Uthe lesi sigameko sidale ifu elimnyana ezweni.&quot;Isinqumo sokususa lezi ziguli eSidimeni kwaku wuku phanjanelwa ingqondo kwezikhulu zoMnyango wezeMpilo eGoli,&quot; kusho uMotsoaledi etshela amalungu ePhalamende.Uthe umnyango kazwelonke wawungazi lutho ngalolu hlelo, wazi ngesikade ukuthi inhloso yokwenza lokhu kwakungukonga imali yoMnyango wesifundazwe.UMotsoaledi uthe lesi sizathu sokuthi kwakongiwa imali senza udaba lokufa kweziguli lube lubi buhlungu kakhulu.